body.description: In a world where your mobile device is your constant companion, you deserve a phone that's not just a gadget but a seamless part of your life. Product parameters: CPU: Snapdragon 888 processor. Memory: 8GB of RAM +512GB ROM Battery Capacity: 6000mAh battery Camera: 13MP front camera + 48MP triple rear camera Screen Size: 6.8-inch Operating System: Android 13 Screen Type: Full High Definition (FHD) Provides 2 SIM card slots and 1 TF card slot for versatile connectivity and storage options. Supports both facial recognition and fingerprint unlocking for enhanced security. Resolution: 3040x1440 pixels. Screen Refresh Rate: 90Hz Phone Dimensions: 6.57 x 3.15 x 0.35 inches. Weight: 7.48 ounces Frequency Bands: Supports multiple network bands, including GSM850/900/1800/1900MHz, 3G: WCDMA850/1900/2100MHz, 4G: B1.B2.B4.B5.B7.B8.B20.B28A.B28B.B40, 5G: n260.n261.n258. Network Compatibility: Compatible with GSM, 3G WCDMA, 4G, and 5G networks. Not compatible with CDMA networks. Supported operators：T-Mobile, BTC, MetroPCS, H2O, Movistar, Telcel, Tigo, Claro, Vivacom, Ultra Mobile, lycamobile, Tello Mobile, Bell Wireless, Rogers Wireless, Chatr, Luck Mobile, Virgin Mobile, Telus, Fido, FIZZ, Shaw Mobile, etc. Please note that this device is not compatible with CDMA carriers such as Verizon, Sprint, Boost Mobile, or U.S. Cellular. Additionally, it may not work with new SIM cards from AT&T and Cricket Wireless carriers. Accessories: 1 charger, headphones, phone case, screen protector Elevate your mobile experience with this exceptional phone that adapts to your life, wherever it takes you. Whether you're capturing priceless memories, staying connected with loved ones, or exploring the world through your screen, this phone is your trusty companion.
